  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_137",
    "english": "Among the orcs of the Demon Realm, they have superior battle skills and take on bodyguard missions. They have made their body slim, which is rare for an orc, and have both the style that comes from wearing a business suit, and the barbarity of swinging an oni club.",
